                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "yes_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Let me cool off",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Do you feel it, challenger? The spire keeps its own ledger — every idle minute on my stair banks another coal, and you lingered."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Whatever my wardens vented, you let the coals reignite. The forge runs at full draft now. No mercy rate, no discounts — the whole fire, all at once."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Vulcan — the coals reignited",
                    Label: "banked"
                }
            ]
        },
